                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13844708" author="adela" created="Tue, 10 Dec 2013 21:49:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The current approach assigns the regions in round robin fashion, but taking the racks into consideration (for each rack, for each regionserver , we assign a region). And we always start with the same rack. Additional improvement is to merge all regionservers together and then do the round robin assignment which would give us balance per regionserver. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
